column1: Thanks to JC Perez and the Pitbull Gym staff for putting this meet on and working so hard to cater
to the lifters. As you can see from the meet results we had many lifter breaking records. Great plaques
were given out as awards. The meet ran in a efficient manner and was well worth the trip for many lifters to
Pitbull. Thanks to our judges Tom O Donnell, Andrew and Molly.
